  "root_text": {
    "an4.66:0.1": "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4.66 ",
    "an4.66:0.2": "7. Pattakammavagga ",
    "an4.66:0.3": "Sarāgasutta ",
    "an4.66:1.1": "“Cattārome, bhikkhave, puggalā santo saṁvijjamānā lokasmiṁ. ",
    "an4.66:1.2": "Katame cattāro? ",
    "an4.66:1.3": "Sarāgo, sadoso, samoho, samāno—",
    "an4.66:1.4": "Ime kho, bhikkhave, cattāro puggalā santo saṁvijjamānā lokasminti. ",
    "an4.66:2.1": "Sārattā rajanīyesu, ",
    "an4.66:2.2": "Piyarūpābhinandino; ",
    "an4.66:2.3": "Mohena āvutā sattā, ",
    "an4.66:2.4": "Baddhā vaḍḍhenti bandhanaṁ. ",
    "an4.66:3.1": "Rāgajaṁ dosajañcāpi, ",
    "an4.66:3.2": "mohajaṁ cāpaviddasū; ",
    "an4.66:3.3": "Karontākusalaṁ kammaṁ, ",
    "an4.66:3.4": "savighātaṁ dukhudrayaṁ. ",
    "an4.66:4.1": "Avijjānivutā posā, ",
    "an4.66:4.2": "andhabhūtā acakkhukā; ",
    "an4.66:4.3": "Yathā dhammā tathā santā, ",
    "an4.66:4.4": "na tassevanti maññare”ti. ",
    "an4.66:4.5": "Chaṭṭhaṁ. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "an4.66:0.1": "Numbered Discourses 4.66 ",
    "an4.66:0.2": "7. Fitting Deeds ",
    "an4.66:0.3": "Greedy ",
    "an4.66:1.1": "“Mendicants, these four individuals are found in the world. ",
    "an4.66:1.2": "What four? ",
    "an4.66:1.3": "The greedy, the hateful, the delusional, and the conceited. ",
    "an4.66:1.4": "These are the four individuals found in the world. ",
    "an4.66:2.1": "Full of desire for desirable things, ",
    "an4.66:2.2": "enjoying things that seem pleasant, ",
    "an4.66:2.3": "beings veiled by delusion ",
    "an4.66:2.4": "only tighten their bonds. ",
    "an4.66:3.1": "Born of greed, born of hate, ",
    "an4.66:3.2": "born of delusion: the ignorant ",
    "an4.66:3.3": "do unskillful deeds ",
    "an4.66:3.4": "that afflict and produce pain. ",
    "an4.66:4.1": "If you act out of these qualities, <j>that’s what you become. ",
    "an4.66:4.2": "But men shrouded by ignorance, ",
    "an4.66:4.3": "are blind, with no eyes to see, ",
    "an4.66:4.4": "and they never imagine that this could be so.” "
  },
  "variant_text": {
    "an4.66:0.3": "Sarāgasutta → sarāga (puggala) suttaṁ (bj) ",
    "an4.66:2.3": "Mohena āvutā sattā → adhamā sattā (bj, cck, sya1ed, km); adhamasattā (sya2ed, pts1ed) ",
    "an4.66:2.4": "Baddhā → bandhā (mr) ",
    "an4.66:3.3": "kammaṁ → dhammaṁ (mr) ",
    "an4.66:4.4": "tassevanti → nassevanti (bj) "
  },
